Project Title
CalmMind AI â€“ Mental Wellness Support Chatbot using Prompt Engineering

Overview
CalmMind AI is a mental wellness chatbot designed to provide emotional support, stress-relief guidance, and a safe conversational space.
The bot prioritizes empathy, emotional safety, and ethical AI boundaries.

Objectives
-Provide emotional support
-Encourage healthy coping strategies
-Create a calm, non-judgmental environment
-Promote seeking professional help when needed

Target Users
-Students facing stress
-Working professionals
-Individuals seeking emotional calm

Prompt Strategy
-Safety-first prompt design
-Explicit restrictions on diagnosis and medical advice
-Focus on validation and listening

Tone Control
-Calm
-Gentle
-Reassuring
-Non-judgmental
-Tone is controlled through words like empathetic, supportive, and reassuring.

Ethical Boundaries
-NOT a replacement for therapy
-No medical or psychiatric advice
-Encourages professional support when necessary

Skills Demonstrated
-Prompt Engineering
-Emotional Tone Control
-Ethical AI Design
-Conversational Safety
